# Welcome to {{DOMAIN}}'s new Gemini server!

If you can see this, it means Grackle is serving the contents of /home/gemini/app/public/ with the Unsinkable Molly Brown.

Use the "gemini" account to manage your Gemini files with SFTP. If you need to do this with the shell, run "grapp shell-on gemini" to enable shell access.
